garage.model.garage

Class Lot

  • java.lang.Object
    • garage.model.garage.Lot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Lot
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Lot class stores the levels within the parking lot system and its spaces. There can only be one instance of a Lot object at any given point once instantiated. It'll create the levels and spaces based on how many are needed for each one. Along with creating spaces, it'll also open them and close them based on their current state of usage.
    Version:
    1.0 Dec. 17, 2017.
    Author:
    Feng Parra
